SAVERIO POLLONI

   about the Art of Saverio Polloni: "Pop icons of the natural world,
   always portraied in real life size, posing in a indefinite space with
   no perspective and looking at you. Painted in a flemish reinaissance
   accuracy with a contemporary design flavor and a touch of irony" Bernie
   Rhodenbarr

